text: Novy Arslan () is a rural locality (a village) in Bishkurayevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 19 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 63 km from Tuymazy, 18 km from Bishkurayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Novy Arslan
